---
title: Recent Posts
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
permalink: "| /blog/"
---

section
    each post in collections.post
        article(class="my-10")
            h2(class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-900 mb-2 dark:text-gray-400")
                a(href=post.url) #{ post.data.title }
            p(class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-500 mb-3 dark:text-white") Published
                time #{ filters.readableDate(post.date) } 
                | by
                | #{ post.data.author }
            if post.data.description
                p(class="text-lg text-gray-500 mb-3 dark:text-white") #{ post.data.description }
                a(href=post.url class="text-slate-500 font-bold text-lg") Read more â†’